data.title: Post Your Literary Collections
data.text:
Originally posted by Lady Tesser

I think if I listed all the titles in our library (yes, there is enough to fill up an entire room with nothing but bookshelves), it will take up at least 10 posts. PCT and I are bibliophiles, and we'll probably be killed by our books burying us alive. Originally posted by Lady Tesser
